    "body": "thanks, so I guess this is more of a stackoverflow question or rfc-issue than a rust-issue:\n\n@Undeterminant: you can implement what you want along those lines:\n\n``` rust\nimpl Broken {\n    fn decompose(&mut self) -> (&mut usize, &DoesNotCopy) {\n        (&mut self.x, &self.y)\n    }\n\n    fn do_stuff(&mut self) -> (usize, &DoesNotCopy) {\n        let (ref mut x, ref y) = self.decompose();\n        (std::mem::replace(x, 0), y)\n    }\n}\n```\n\n[Playpen](http://is.gd/Gvx9ZD)\n",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
