    "body": "Or more close: http://is.gd/zpMUkp\n\n``` rust\nstruct DoesNotCopy(usize);\n\nstruct Broken {\n    x: usize,\n    y: DoesNotCopy\n}\n\nimpl Broken {\n    fn decompose(&self) -> (usize, &DoesNotCopy) {\n        (self.x, &self.y)\n    }\n\n    fn do_stuff(&mut self) -> (usize, &DoesNotCopy) {\n        let (ref mut x, ref y) = self.decompose();\n        (std::mem::replace(x, 0), y)\n    }\n}\n```\n\nNice job!\n",
