    "created_at": "2016-07-14T14:39:53Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-07-14T14:39:53Z",
    "body": "Just for reference. The following compiles now\n\n```\nstruct DoesNotCopy(usize);\n\nstruct Broken {\n    x: usize,\n    y: DoesNotCopy,\n}\n\nimpl Broken {\n    fn decompose(&mut self) -> (usize, &DoesNotCopy) {\n        let &mut Broken {mut x, ref mut y} = self;\n        (x, y)\n    }\n\n    fn do_stuff(&mut self) -> (usize, &DoesNotCopy) {\n        let (mut x, mut y) = self.decompose();\n        x = 0;\n        (x, y)\n    }\n}\n```\n\nhttps://gist.github.com/38b7e06f15ad75ac3da66521dc7baa29\n",
